Alias          MyD*+      D*+
Alias          MyD*-      D*-
ChargeConj     MyD*-      MyD*+

Alias          MyD0       D0
Alias          Myanti-D0  anti-D0
ChargeConj     MyD0       Myanti-D0

#
Decay B0sig
  1.000 MyD*- pi+ SVS;
Enddecay
CDecay anti-B0sig
#
Decay MyD*-
  1.000 Myanti-D0 pi- VSS;
Enddecay
CDecay MyD*+
#
## Disable PHOTOS for all AmpGen models
noPhotos
Decay Myanti-D0
  1.000 K+ pi- pi- pi+ LbAmpGen DtoKpipipi;
Enddecay
CDecay MyD0
End
